description:
It's the Golf Capital of the World. What better place for 12 aspiring tour pros to put their skills to the test? This season, six men and six women will compete as individuals in a series of head to head challenges. And the pressure is on. First prize is a chance to play with the very best on the PGA or LPGA tour. May the best man, or woman, win.




Big Break: Myrtle Beach - Season 22, Episode 1



Super Immunity

Six women and six men arrive on the Grand Strand and find out key information about the competition. The players compete for a season-long Super Immunity prize, which could give one competitor a distinct advantage over his/her opponents. Hosted by Tom Abbott and Paige Mackenzie from Barefoot Resort & Golf in Myrtle Beach, SC.



Original Air Date: 07-Oct-2014
